thod strings.\n\nIt's a bit unclear, so I might need to adjust my assertions. Perhaps making the package-private base class public could help, especially if we want to avoid issues with `getInternalPublicMethods`.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0c59f6ae114282ef0169f0a63e27c48193bea41f77ceb5f996\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp8KZbr4agY3O1OcDf8zdxQlffqKosAX8covwybqFZi8iZ_9hEx0BzhdrFiEaTX9b8QdxwQFQztYlTRSj3BYmGcsaiBrS5l6WdXq3cLsAKFuFR6h9WSFhXJBOaZ60WLIcas5rHqfw1sDVzyg5ziJtg6wj_Yq75egWTjBDwHInB1hi1fX-tfJMnIwlNDLwr9qcQTYs5_sNxmKXdTn_j32AZ4h2YnOcvWjy603DJpxljA34ANviFtzzk-Zj5--L9gZNr3Nn96anZ92aqavAZfiLVlT3sVrXZVx-HGcaZSbnOGo9p3GobfkhCtImkkC27Cx9VlPr6szTploXJIuW4e0XgfXc4KknL6vZpBfjU_Vudh8_TN_PhM9EbsML9dhXfMTZ9wVdG6yPn8XJmpFbJhEOmeN-m3geP9lbSoqL7paJeYgNsGsFGB9xTquXTKabOaxQreqQW9u-gREnGbjAI48_iAg8l6ImLbZ4uywJvgi5BLYXfIkScmaegqfHDvMfV2CqU95pcgFOsDTLAXGnmCPskp03KmfdzlkrfSHe1b8N8RyoCs00QHBKqbUxWyIhd_D_FaTNzKLMRTJFdpJ-OeneDs9Hl0szxmQSVBr8Vrmg9iBorqIhpqk15NS7ToRnUurOkqv8D6WuLYkZE6PzvqvUJ3gtv7q-bZatqgrKz8tWOI7QX-YL45wwer2r7OyLZ-jbLBwygHuMRPQpdP3rTh_YyDYOn4xzuVQcG80c3qzPv7rMtNBhFB7gk4jy_xc7irafq3eE_-sCzBOBR2FfXOr1h6b_O7PpNELmKaJBtIdpwpscLX-ZDP5x0Z1Dit6fZZ0ybn1Y2LuS_ipFAoh_jBBpYB4aIOlWVJTaPjnpndThQtRXIt_lmJhYqS97TutTsSjnty-clPWtw-YePgJy1ZyJg3CXhlnQOzg5jKwyQZGhUolIGUILEZzacrW_oon1pIdMf3AhY-ap9nMOB7EmJj7NYpba2JrRu1jtkUQHMJb7sXbuRbV4u-wuYhba-9CQfeSQDapasKzRNmpUwnr8hSsBvf8kBtmYdqWDl-TQlVKSe0bTx555XF2SMtEP4-v5p47VQkTt1RaV97KboBzpyKPaKRTicT39SqTSRnWexqVra1tGwQTRe68mfUXx61iWy-tBHpXjXmUK6NqLoOvSRngoEhhI0O24jXKameINi259uS-gKI6iTTT5A_zVBs9tm0ghgCGPmLcYG8_or0to59wCQI9fui8r4J0wKeXQmp4AFcJzEA40dnWcTrhAtizNXbj0izSlH2p1UhyDrm-nVC-QlMwn0tvaSuaTo9uhj6dtAcPNdAn_VsDtXgmZ9BfzY-2CmQATzEidvXiNxg_C1FWKX79kYKTwqQTGZ2e-ehW0G-xgBI0r1BCGdCdzhDu4MQ68ipqA6FeHsUh5WBHJOAh9SRgFroCIEIwliKO7J8yuet_9A6BMbciOBiXnG-gY2pIFBSjaaO032hwvLJn_crm8TgFYWeNe0JsBMqCNJETRcygJ5E8LDoH9US1gmp6mffoLBAJmdRqVbZrrFkvZlAG2QZtuHDVVZHDV1PbSuuFPByhkWYOtanHc3vIpGlNdi1X_dPdF2cnEKF0Y9-VC1jzbxksZ9pakadsFbGJcM4Fuf3